    "body": "`.cmd` needs to be appended to the path if you are trying to spawn it from `node_modules\\.bin`, this is a limitation of node's spawn command.\r\n\r\nYou can confirm this by running `child_process.spawn` directly from Node with and without the `.cmd` suffix.\r\n\r\nClosing this out, adding `.cmd` should address this or obtain the path of the running Electron instance with `process.execPath`."
